# Gemini CLI ignore list (repo-local).
#
# Purpose: keep Gemini context and file tool access fast and predictable, while
# still allowing workflow artifacts under `.tmp/agent-workflow/`.
#
# NOTE: We intentionally do NOT ignore `.tmp/` here because workflow artifacts
# live under `.tmp/agent-workflow/` and are required for plan/acceptance work.

node_modules/
dist/
build/
.out/
.next/
coverage/
.cache/
.DS_Store
*.log
.env
.env.*
